<br />
<br />"So I see this is your first time playing a Castlevania game....."
<br />
<br />Not much more to say than that.  I read the thing in full -- twice -- and I had a hard time taking away anything beneficial/useful, development or design-wise, from it.
<br />
<br />This sort of bollocks is exactly why I don't do console development and stuff any longer.  Continually "analysing" video games, for me anyway, takes away from the overall enjoyment / fun aspect.  I'm much happier just playing them.  :D

		

